{#  EXAMPLE:

## [X.Y.Z] - YYYY-MM-DD

_This release is published under the MIT License._       # Release Notes Only

- Initial Release

    Emit the same Keep-a-Changelog bracketed heading as versioned_changes.md.j2
    (## [X.Y.Z] - DATE, no 'v' prefix) so the init path matches the house
    format and the heading resolves against the '[X.Y.Z]:' footer link.

#}{{
"## [%s] - %s\n" | format(
    release.version | string,
    release.tagged_date.strftime("%Y-%m-%d")
)
}}{%  if license_name is defined and license_name
%}{{    "\n_This release is published under the %s License._\n" | format(license_name)
}}{%  endif
%}
- Initial Release
